timelineItems.desc:
Toronto FC playmaker Sebastian Giovinco is among the smaller players in MLS, but his strength, quickness and sublime skills earned him the nickname "Atomic Ant" during his time with Juventus FC and Italy's national team. Teammates Jozy Altidore and Michael Bradley call him "Seba" and laud his qualities.

MLS Insider Presented by adidas dives into the story lines behind Major League Soccer. Your favorite players. Your favorite teams. Unprecedented access.
timelineItems.title: The Atomic Ant | MLS Insider Presented by adidas
